ustralia|Liberal]] || South Australia || 1968 || 1950\u20131967\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Bill|Heatley}} {{efn|name=Sherrington}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || Queensland || 1966,{{efn|name=Appointment}} 1968 || 1966\u20131968\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Bert|Hendrickson}} || {{Australian party style|Labor}}|&nbsp; || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] || Victoria || 1971 || 1947\u20131971\n|-\n|| {{sort|Henty, Denham|Hon. [[Denham Henty]]}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || Tasmania || 1968 || 1950\u20131968\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Jim|Keeffe}} || {{Australian party style|Labor}}|&nbsp; || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] || Queensland || 1971 || 1965\u20131983\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Pat|Kennelly}} || {{Australian party style|Labor}}|&nbsp; || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] || Victoria || 1971 || 1953\u20131971\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Bert|Lacey}} || {{Australian party style|Labor}}|&nbsp; || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] || Tasmania || 1971 || 1965\u20131971\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Condor|Laucke}} {{efn|name=Hannaford}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || South Australia || 1968 {{efn|name=Appointment}} || 1967\u20131981\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Keith|Laught}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || South Australia || 1971 || 1951\u20131969\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Ellis|Lawrie}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || Queensland || 1971 || 1965\u20131975\n|-\n|| {{sortname|Elliot|Lillico}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || Tasmania || 1971 || 1959\u20131974\n|-\n|| {{sortname|John|Marriott|John Marriott (Australian politician)}} || {{Australian party style|Liberal}}|&nbsp; || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] || Tasmania || 1971 || 1953\u20131975\n|-\n|| {{sort|Mattner, Ted|Hon. [[